data.description: This beautiful 1-story home, nestled on a cul-de-sac in Cimarron Landing, is ready to be yours! Featuring a light and bright open floor plan with high ceilings and a spacious living room that flows seemlessly into the kitchen, complete with a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and dining nook, and primary bedroom with back yard views and full bath. Updates include water softener, central vaccum and outside speakers. The backyard hosts a covered patio, lawn, treetop views and privacy fence. You will love the location, close to parks, schools, 1604 and Randolph AFB. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your next home, book your tour today!
